---
---

<section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="about-container reveal-up">
        <div class="about-content">
            <h2 class="about-title">"프론티어웍스는 '기술'을 자랑하지 않습니다. <br><span class="highlight">'작동하는 결과물'</span>로 증명합니다."</h2>
            <p class="about-text">
                우리는 AI가 단지 트렌드에 머물지 않도록, 교육 현장의 워크플로우 속에
                자연스럽게 녹아들어 실질적인 변화를 일으키는 도구를 만듭니다.
            </p>
            <p class="about-signature">
                <span class="logo-frontier">Frontier</span><span class="logo-works">Works</span>: We make it work.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-visual">
            <div class="tech-circle">
                <div class="core">AI</div>
                <div class="orbit">
                    <div class="node n1"><span>Edu</span></div>
                    <div class="node n2"><span>Work</span></div>
                    <div class="node n3"><span>Auto</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .about {
        padding: 8rem 2rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(3, 7, 18, 0.95));
    }

    .about-container {
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border-radius: 32px;
        padding: 4rem;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 4rem;
    }

    .about-container::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 60%;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-brand-works), transparent);
    }

    .about-title {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-family: var(--font-ko);
    }

    .about-text {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: var(--color-text-secondary);
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto 3rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .about-signature {
        font-family: var(--font-en);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        border-radius: 50px;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    /* Tech Circle */
    .about-visual {
        width: 300px;
        height: 300px;
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .tech-circle {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .core {
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent-1), var(--color-accent-2));
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        font-family: var(--font-en);
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(79, 172, 254, 0.5);
        z-index: 2;
        position: relative;
    }

    .core::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: -10px;
        left: -10px;
        right: -10px;
        bottom: -10px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        border: 1px dashed rgba(79, 172, 254, 0.5);
        animation: rotate-reverse 10s linear infinite;
    }

    .orbit {
        position: absolute;
        width: 240px;
        height: 240px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 50%;
        animation: rotate 15s linear infinite;
    }

    .node {
        position: absolute;
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        background: var(--color-surface);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        font-family: var(--font-en);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        top: -25px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        animation: rotate-reverse 15s linear infinite;
    }

    .n1 { transform-origin: center 145px; transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(0deg); }
    .n2 { transform-origin: center 145px; transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(120deg); }
    .n3 { transform-origin: center 145px; transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(240deg); }

    .n1 > span, .n2 > span, .n3 > span {
        animation: rotate-reverse 15s linear infinite;
        display: block;
    }

    @keyframes rotate {
        100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
    }

    @keyframes rotate-reverse {
        100% { transform: rotate(-360deg); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .about-container {
            padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
        }
        .about-title {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
        }
    }

    @media (min-width: 900px) {
        .about-container {
            flex-direction: row;
            text-align: left;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .about-container::before {
            left: 0;
            transform: none;
            width: 2px;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, var(--color-brand-works), transparent);
        }
        .about-text {
            margin: 0 0 3rem 0;
        }
    }
</style>
